<h1>Help</h1>
<p>
  If you have forgotten your password, please post your concerns on the wall for
  <a href="www.facebook.com">Chat Cal Poly</a>'s
  Facebook page.
  <br>
  <br>
  In addition, uploading profile photos through Gravatar.com allows the site to become more user-friendly, so please
  don't hesitate especially since it is a free service.  Just provide your email address, a password, and a photo!
 
</p>
